Package: ProteomicsR
Title: Multi-Organ Proteomics Analysis Pipeline
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Leong", "Ng", email = "lln1@leicester.ac.uk", role = c("aut")),
    person("Marta", "Nascimento", email = "marta.parente.nascimento@outlook.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A multi-organ proteomics analysis pipeline supporting imputation
    (missForest or half-minimum), batch correction via RUViii-PRPS, differential
    expression with limma/voom, and QC visualizations including RLE plots, PCA,
    volcano plots, and heatmaps.
